net.proteusframework.core.script

Class GroovyScriptContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.core.script.GroovyScriptContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    groovy.lang.GroovyObject, ScriptContext

    public class GroovyScriptContext
extends Object
implements ScriptContext, groovy.lang.GroovyObject
    ScriptContext that is a GroovyObject.

    This allows groovy style property access to attributes in the ScriptContext. This also allows execution of attribute values that are executable such as a method or closure.

    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
